Project Name: Historie ofte Iaerlijck Verhael van de Verrichtinghen der Geoctroyeerde West-Indische Compagnie
Author: Laet, Joannes de, 1593-1649
Name.subject: West-Indische Compagnie (Netherlands)
Title: Historie ofte Iaerlijck verhael van de verrichtinghen der Geoctroyeerde West-Indische Compagnie, zedert haer begin, tot het eynde van 't jaer sesthien-hondert ses-en-dertich : begrepen in derthien boecken, ende met verscheyden koperen platen verciert / beschreven door Ioannes de Laet, Bewint-hebber der selver Compagnie.
Description.abstract: Following the introduction, which includes the charter and a listing of the shareholders, there are 544 pages covering the thirteen annual reports, followed by 31 pages of profit and loss statements and then 13 pages of an index.
Format.extent: 16 p. l., 544, 31, [11] p. 14 double pl. (incl. maps)
AltTitle.translated: Annual report of the activities of the incorporated West-Indian Company from its beginning in the year 1623 through the year 1636 in 13 books with illustrations
Description.note: Of the thirteen illustrations, which had to be included manually, four are missing.
